{"tid":376663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無野重要得過返工】港豬趕返工，呻等巴士耐","createTime":"2017-08-27T07:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T07:48:05.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"291606259bf14883733b3601bc2eb6596ad18cca","tid":376663,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"有市民在紅磡等過海巴士趕返工，等近半小時仍未有車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n任維修工人的陳先生家住新界，他先乘東鐵出紅磡，諗住轉乘隧巴往銅鑼灣上班，但等了15分鐘仍未有車。「公司話要我哋趕住返去開工，但冇公共車輛叫人點返去？冇理由搭的士，冇車都要等。」"},{"pid":"36850c0f7bee2c7de53527f0b97dac7ea9b014c3","tid":376663,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d24d508e135ad7aaca3e64b806607a0da021d30","tid":376663,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"剛才坐mtr去食lunch<br />\n見到勁多人係美孚站趕轉車(西鐵綫去荃灣綫），應該趕返工"},{"pid":"ea09f8d7c32bb3892ed49a50f07d52c4ab7417a4","tid":376663,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d964f0a1891e90db3b1b4d3a98594625c36979a","tid":376663,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗做咩"},{"pid":"1321039234b433e9bfdcc5e5a51cb6e2360fe159","tid":376663,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:48:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}